orance: When to say Allah knows best","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Razin Abi al-Nu\u2019man reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhen you are asked about what you do not know, then flee.\u201d It was said, \u201cO leader of the faithful, how does one flee?\u201d Ali said, \u201cThat you say: Allah knows best.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30357,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/20\/ali-beware-gates-sultan\/","url_meta":{"origin":32798,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Rulers: Beware of the gates of the ruler","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bayhaqi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cBeware of the gates of the ruler.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 8790 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0647\u0642\u064a \u0648\u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0627\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064f\u0644\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 8790 \u0634\u0639\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646 \u0644\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0647\u0642\u064a","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/salat-al-witr-ahl-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":32798,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Witr prayer recommended, not obligation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is numerically odd and He loves what is odd, so perform the Witr prayer, O people of the Quran!\u201d Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe Witr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-ibn-abu-talib-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":32798,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Curses: Those who curse others are themselves cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubayd al-Kindi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThose who curse others are themselves cursed.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 315 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0646\u062f\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0639\u0644\u064a \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0637\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u200f \u0644\u064f\u0639\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0639\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e 315 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u062